{
  "stem": "15962.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We were directed to pick up some mattresses and move to one of the large rooms of this, of these military barracks.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "These were masonry barracks that was recently occupied by German troops.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as we were trying to do this, I collapsed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my colleagues first said, well, you're being lazy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You don't want to carry mattresses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they soon realized that I just couldn't get up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they carried me across the street to the barrack that was a hospital.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had typhus.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] for several weeks I was just out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had no idea whether I was unconscious or semi-unconscious.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have no recollection.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I know that, sort of vaguely, that everybody ate my food, that I couldn't even eat, and that they were giving me intravenous-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] feeding me intravenously.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Ever since, I just abhor needles or, or any kind of transfusions.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But bit by bit I got stronger, and many of the-- several of the supervisory American staff that supervised German orderlies who were supposed to clean for us and keep-- you know, make beds-- and the medical, American medical staff sought me out because I spoke some English when I was a child.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I took some private English lessons so I could make myself understood.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And several of those gave me their photographs and took my address and gave me theirs.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And months after I finally reached home, we kept in touch and wrote to each other.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And unfortunately, only one of them, the doctor, who was from Baltimore, kept in touch until I came here.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we actually met once.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He died of cancer about five years ago.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
